# Cleaned Data

This directory stores cleaned and processed CSV files that are ready for import into the SQLite database.

## Output Files
- `education_clean.csv`: Cleaned education sector data
- `health_clean.csv`: Cleaned health sector data
- `law_justice_clean.csv`: Cleaned law and justice sector data

## Generated By
- R scripts in the `R/` directory (01-03 series)

## Usage
- These files are imported into SQLite database using SQL scripts
- Do not manually edit these files
- Regenerate by re-running the R cleaning scripts
